# Build-context allowlist for server/web/Dockerfile, whose context is the
# repo root (the arena stack's context is server/arena/, unaffected by this
# file). The repo carries multi-GB desktop build artifacts (apps/desktop/
# src-tauri/target, dist, public), so: exclude everything, re-add only what
# the web build actually consumes. Last matching line wins.
*
!.git
!package.json
!pnpm-lock.yaml
!pnpm-workspace.yaml
!apps/desktop/package.json
!apps/desktop/app
!apps/desktop/hooks
!apps/desktop/lib
!apps/web
apps/web/dist
apps/web/node_modules
apps/web/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
!packages
packages/*/node_modules
!data/personas/*.config.json
!data/personas/*.book.json
!server/web/nginx.conf
